Package: JumpPoisReg
Type: Package
Title: Poisson Regression for Markov and Semi-Markov Jump Paths
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Martin", "Bladt", email = "martinbladt@math.ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Author: Martin Bladt [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Martin Bladt <martinbladt@math.ku.dk>
Description: Fits piecewise Poisson regression models for transition
    intensities from observed jump-process paths under Markov and semi-Markov
    specifications. Includes simulation of jump paths for time-inhomogeneous
    models.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    stats,
    utils
